Subject: drm/i915: Move framestart_delay to crtc_state
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 50c335f94d71c8b68560abf3fe273962111adcaa
